🌌 Stellarix Core

Stellarix Core is the central planning and documentation repository for the Stellarix Discord bot.
It contains all core ideas, feature plans, system design notes, and future roadmap for the project.

🚀 About Stellarix

Stellarix is an advanced, modular Discord bot designed to provide:

⚙️ Powerful utility tools
🎮 Fun and interactive features
🛡️ Moderation systems
📊 Server insights and automation
🧩 Expandable plugin-style architecture

This repository acts as the brain behind Stellarix, not the bot code itself.

📁 What’s in this Repository?

This repo includes:

📌 Feature planning documents
🧠 System architecture ideas
🗺️ Roadmaps and milestones
📝 Design decisions and notes
💡 Experimental concepts
🧭 Project Goals
Build a scalable and modular Discord bot
Keep features well-documented before development
Maintain a clear long-term vision
Make collaboration easier with structured planning
🛠️ Planned Features

Some planned systems include:

🤖 Advanced command system
🧠 AI-powered responses (optional modules)
🎵 Music system
🛡️ Moderation tools (auto-mod, logs, filters)
📈 Leveling / XP system
🎉 Events and mini-games
🔌 Plugin/module system
🗺️ Roadmap
Phase 1 – Foundation
Core architecture planning
Command structure design
Basic moderation system
Phase 2 – Core Features
Utility commands
Leveling system
Logging & analytics
Phase 3 – Expansion
Music system
Games & fun commands
Plugin system
Phase 4 – Advanced Systems
AI integrations
Dashboard (web panel)
Custom server configurations
🤝 Contributing

This repository is mainly for planning, but contributions are welcome!

You can help by:

Suggesting features
Improving documentation
Refining system designs
Opening discussions/issues
📌 Notes
This is not the main bot code repository
Everything here may change as ideas evolve
The goal is clarity before implementation


You can join are discord here to suggest features [here](https://discord.gg/drr4cw8TXq)